<i>noun</i>: 받아쓰기 [바다쓰기] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>받아쓰기 [바다쓰기]</dt><br>
<dd>dictation</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람이 말하거나 읽는 것을 듣고 맞춤법에 맞게 옮겨 쓰는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of listening to what another person says or reads aloud and writing it down, observing grammatical rules.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>